{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"农村辩论会纪事","authors":["燕凌"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":11,"day":25}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农村辩论会纪事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕凌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么回事？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“前天叫你卖余粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说你的产量比社里的少；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天辩论合作化好不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又说你的产量比社里的高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是怎么一回事？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你向大家说分晓！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会场上一阵哈哈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见有个人一言不发把头搔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怨谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今年社里减了产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明年我还要单干！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩世元怒气冲天高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘟嘟囔囔直埋怨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“社里怎么减了产？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别怨地来别怨天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别怨农业合作化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别怨干部心不专。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年麦收大热天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏收工回家转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个社员走得慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拖拉拉在后边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不是打场累着啦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么两腿粗又圆？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社长关心去慰问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一摸可就露了馅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来他两条裤子一齐穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四只裤脚缝住了边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁着人们不留神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子装满了裤脚管。……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“有人下地提上大水罐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人下地提上馍馍篮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"馍馍吃光水喝干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装满谷穗回家转。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们都要这样干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社里怎能不减产？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“还有两个生产队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打场故意轻轻干；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等到社里分配完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄再来打一遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产队里要瞒产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎叫社里不减产？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“夏天苗儿长得欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野草也在往上窜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有些社员离了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弃农从商去赚钱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋田荒了一小半，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎叫社里不减产？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不做农活做商贩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其中就有你韩世元。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想带头闹退社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打着剥削人的铁算盘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这条道儿走不通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁早收起你的摊！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}